*An Guo (安國) 116
*Yi Fu (遺腹) 125
*Chen Pan (臣磐) 127
*He De (和得) 168
*A Mijue (阿彌厥) 605
*Pei Chuo (裴綽) 618
*Pei Amozhi (裴阿摩支) 627
*Pei Yijian (裴夷健) 698
*Pei Anding (裴安定) 728
*Pei Guoliang (裴國良) 753
*Pei Lengleng (裴冷冷) 784–789? / Tang general – Lu Yang (魯陽) 789

